data.description:
Beautiful House For Executives,Professionals,Insurance personals and Students to Share (DRA)


What?? Two master suites?? YES! 1 upstairs and 1 downstairs! This gorgeous 4 Bed, 3.5 Bath, 3 Car Garage attached house  located in an area close to all the amenities " you name it you have it " (freeway, restaurants, banks, Home Depot, parks, etc., etc.) It's nestled among other beautiful homes in a great neighborhood!! Lots of room to grow in this beauty. Gorgeous, easy to maintain tile flooring, beautiful large kitchen with designer leaded glass in cabinet doors. So many options here. Close to shopping and restaurants. Tucked back in a quiet community.


Please feel free to drive by the property in the Neighborhood first,  Fill up,Complete & Submit a Free online Rental application using the link below.

                 https://ezstop.managebuilding.com/Resident/apps/rentalapp

Then Call SAM 916 601 6952 / 916 363 9500 to schedule viewing or further Info.

Lease terms
~Tenant pays for Water
~Tenant  pays @ $ 95 per month a flat fee for sewer and garbage.
~Pets Negotiable
~Credit history and past rental references will be checked.
~A Non Refundable $35 Per Adult credit & criminal check fee will be charged to Qualified Tenant Only.
